    "description": "If you're a passionate Process Engineer with drive and ambition, Baidyanath Asia Pacific Associates in Jaipur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Baidyanath Asia Pacific Associates:\nBaidyanath Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Baidyanath Asia Pacific Associates!",
